Ansys Shares Surge to Five-Month High on Earnings Increase

-- B y   S t e p h e n   G u n n i o n
-- 
2011-10-10T15:28:18Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-10/ansys-shares-surge-to-highest-in-five-months-on-earnings-gain.html
Ansys Ltd. (ANS) , a designer of transport
and defense-monitoring systems, climbed to its highest in almost
five months in Johannesburg trading after saying earnings per
share rose to as much as 4.47 cents in the six months to Aug.
31, from 0.21 cents a year earlier.  The shares advanced 26 percent to close at 34 cents as of
5 p.m., the highest since May 13.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Stephen Gunnion in Johannesburg at 
